name: Wuta
Lore: 'Ewok explorer. Scout. Searches for fallen trees to make tools. Tracks predators. First to notice the Imperial presence on Endor.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Endor. Power and forfeit +1 for each [Light Side Force] icon at same Endor site. Once during each of your deploy phases, if at an exterior Endor site, may use 2 Force to deploy an Endor site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
